  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1:   \u0b86\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sexual assault on multiple female students: Probation extended to teacher",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The case against a 28-year-old teacher, who was arrested on the charge of sexually abusing some female students in Mullaitivu, was taken up for hearing today (30) at the Mullaitivu District Magistrate's Court.",
        "The investigation has revealed that a teacher of a school in Mullaitivu fell in love with students, took nude and sexually explicit photos of 6 students, showed them to students, threatened them and sexually abused them.",
        "The visa was taken through video technology in the presence of Mullaitivu District Magistrate Judge R. Saravanaraja. The magistrate ordered the suspect to be kept in remand.",
        "Following the confession obtained by the Mullaitivu Police from six students in connection with this case, all the six students have been subjected to an examination by the forensic officer. It has been revealed that two students have been sexually abused.",
        "Mullaitivu Police have filed two more charges (rape charges) against the teacher, the suspect in the case.",
        "The magistrate, who directed the suspect to appear in court on the 7th for the hearing of these two cases, today (30) granted bail to the student who was placed on remand under the charge of aiding and abetting the teacher's sexual activity.",
        "The first case against the suspect teacher will be taken up in court on the 14th, Mullaitivu police said."
      ],
